    "56168354": {
      "title": "Global well-posedness in the critical Besov spaces for the incompressible Oldroyd-B model without damping mechanism",
      "abstract": "We prove the global well-posedness in the critical Besov spaces for the incompressible Oldroyd-B model without damping mechanism on the stress tensor in $${\\mathbb {R}}^d$$ ::: for the small initial data. Our proof is based on the observation that the behaviors of Green’s matrix to the system of $$\\big (u,(-\\Delta )^{-\\frac{1}{2}}{\\mathbb {P}}\\nabla \\cdot \\tau \\big )$$ ::: as well as the effects of $$\\tau $$ ::: change from the low frequencies to the high frequencies and the construction of the appropriate energies in different frequencies."
    }
